# Build Commands
1- ./bootstrap
you should see "INFO  :: *** Done!" at the end

2- ./configure --enable-local
check progress for missing stuff,  like help2man, then you should install it
sudo apt install help2man # ubuntu
sudo pacman -S help2man # arch
etc
or any package were missed
once you did then no need to check again

3- make

to change build config
4- ./ct-ng menuconfig

to start the build
5- ./ct-ng build
